Introduction

Oh Ha Young is a South Korean Singer, songwriter, actress under Choi Creative Lab. Hayoung is the Vocalist and Youngest Member of the Girl Group APINK.

Hayoung debuted as a member of Apink on April 19, 2011.

She made her solo debut with the album "OH!" on August 21, 2019.

On May 9, 2023, she debuted as a member of the virtual project group FE:VERSE under the name Seoritae.
